name: Roy Tang
text: Prepared sya sumagot e, with facts/figures to back up. Sensible naman yung mga tinatanong nya. Weak lang talaga sya on certain points (like whenever mabanggit si Abaya lol). Poe may mga poor answers and malabong logic. Duterte parang lasing minsan kung sumagot (aside from my usual concern about his predisposition to violence) lol. Binay parang dapat wag na lang umattend sa sunod na debate, wala ata syang napapala ever haha
